latest_reviews.reviewBody: I love these potatoes but I can’t believe the last time I bought these I only got two big size potatoes and I got the last time a big bag of potatoes so I’m kinda confused I guess but they are good delicious potatoes and I’ll still buy them again..I hope I’ll get the bag of potatoes next time butbig not oh well I’ll settle for the two
There are no sprouts on these seed potatoes. Can buy these anywhere. This is not what was expected on this order
